				<td colspan="2"><span>You can lull the mobs for singles.  (just lull the mobs around your target and your target pull as well if you want, and then hit it with a detrimental song and you should only get the one mob).
<br />

<br />
You can mez mobs to reduce how many are incoming originally.
<br />

<br />
You can try charm pulling sometimes the one you charm will be the only one to come, maybe some around it but now you have a pet that can help for a minute till charm fades.
<br />

<br />
Poster above descrided, chant/swarm kiting pretty well.  You can use the search function on the site to find out more info on those.</span></td>
