				<td colspan="2"><span>Summoned pets dont go away on invis.. charmed pets still break 
<br />

<br />
No its not easier to have your new charmed pet beat down your ex-pet.  You need to do some damage yourself to get the full xps and the ex-pet will be aggro on you, not your new pet.  With drum equipped stack multiple different chants on your near-death-ex-pet and run a pattern.  He will be dead soon.  When he is a tick or 2 away from death by chant... THEN charm his previous target and send it back into the swarm...lather...rinse...repeat
<br />

<br />
Reys</span></td>
